title: NASA's Amazing Perseverance
itunes:title: NASA's Amazing Perseverance
description:
The Perseverance Mars rover is already returning incredible video and audio from the Red Planet. We learn about the mission, how it survived massive changes at NASA and what we hope it finds while far away from home.
